entry.title: $2399 // Amazingly huge 2BR1.5BA around the corner from the Central M NO FEE
entry.content:
===\\\**^**^**^**NO FEE!!!**^**^**^**///===

Amazingly huge Two bedroom and One and a half bathroom apartment around the corner from the Central M train, and quick to L train and Myrtle-Broadway JMZ Express. Apartment only 10 minutes from NYC. In a prime location with 24 hour laundry a block away, Bars, Cafes, eateries, markets, and so much shopping its incredible.

Apartment is a private home with two Queen sized bedrooms with big windows and closets. The master suite has a half bathroom attached to it. The apartment itself has a lot of closet space and has a real house feel with a massive living room and Eat-In-Kitchen. Has a vintage feel to it if you're looking for the homey comfortable style. This is a place you would stay a while. Private local landlord, very friendly. This apartment is No Fee, No Pets, and is One months rent and Security.
